-- Bernanke Says Fed Takes ‘Balanced Approach’ to Jobs, Inflation
-- B y   C h r i s   W e l l i s z
-- 2012-02-07T15:50:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-07/bernanke-says-fed-takes-balanced-approach-to-jobs-inflation.html
Federal Reserve Chairman  Ben S.
Bernanke  said the central bank takes a “balanced approach” to
its dual mandate from Congress and doesn’t favor maximum
employment over  price stability .  He spoke in response to questions today during a hearing
before the Senate Budget Committee in  Washington .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chris Wellisz in Washington at 
